  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionTimerActivity
    Abstract class we implement for woodchopping, fishing, and combat.
    ArmoryActivity
    Armory Activity page which allows the user to upgrade their woodchopping, fishing, and/or combat gear
    AttributesActivity
    Abstract class we implement for woodchopping, fishing, and combat.
    CendanaForestTimerActivity
    Cendana Forest Activity page where the user can idly chop down trees to gain wood resource
    EcopondTimerActivity
    Ecopond Activity page where the user can idly fish for fish to gain fish resource
    MarketplaceActivity
    Marketplace Activity where the user can post and accept trades for resources from other users
    SagaBattlegroundTimerActivity
    Saga Battleground Activity page where the user can idly battle monsters to gain gold resource
